casebody.data:
Monday, May 14, 2001

MOTION DOCKET

00-895. State v. Olvera.

Williams App. Nos. WM-98-022 and WM-98-023. This cause came on for further consideration upon appellant’s request for findings of fact/conclusions of law. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the request for findings of facVconclusions of law be, and hereby is, denied.
